00:20:44,560 --> 00:20:44,880
Time:

440
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:47,600
Afternoon, 3rd to 6th October 1917

441
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:49,920
Location: Peking University Liberal Arts Small Auditorium

442
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:51,600
3rd October, First lecture:

443
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,560
The Spirit of Chinese People

444
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:55,200
4th October, Second lecture: The Language of China

445
00:20:55,600 --> 00:20:57,600
5th October, Third lecture: The Women of China

446
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:00,080
6th October, Fourth lecture: Chinese Thought

447
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:03,120
Welcoming current teachers and students to enthusiastically join.

448
00:21:03,760 --> 00:21:06,480
Old Guo, I heard Professor Gu

449
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,920
is now in Dongjiaomin Lane

450
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:10,160
giving foreigners a talk about the Spirit of Chinese People.

451
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:12,720
A ticket is two silver dollars.

452
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:14,880
It's even more expensive than Mei Lanfang's ticket price.

453
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:15,840
Is it true?

454
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:16,720
That's made up!

455
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:19,360
When this Gu Hongming is lecturing at Peking University, no one attends at all.

456
00:21:19,840 --> 00:21:20,800
Still selling tickets?

457
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:21,840
It's true.

458
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,840
When I was a private tutor at a foreigner's house at Dongjiaominxiang,

459
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,360
Professor Gu's reputation was pretty big.

460
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,400
They all said,

461
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,000
coming to China you don't need to see the Three Great Halls,

462
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,440
but you can't not see Gu Hongming.

463
00:21:29,840 --> 00:21:30,400
You see.

464
00:21:30,640 --> 00:21:31,360
This has never-

465
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:33,007
Mr. Zhongfu!

466
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,157
Greetings Mr. Zhongfu

467
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,600
Greetings Mr. Xingyan

468
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,240
Sir, sir.

469
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,160
Look, Gu Hongming wants to start a series of lectures now.

470
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,320
He's not going to use the lectures to promote monarchism again, is he?

471
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:43,680
Don't talk nonsense.

472
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,280
Professor Gu is going to teach knowledge.

473
00:21:45,680 --> 00:21:46,400
Whatever he's going to talk about,

474
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:48,000
just go attend, then you will know right?

475
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,400
Sir, can I attend?

476
00:21:50,800 --> 00:21:52,720
Although Peking University doesn't admit female students right now,

477
00:21:53,200 --> 00:21:56,720
but these type of academic lectures should allow them.

478
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:04,480
Students,

479
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:07,440
I hope everybody will be able to go attend.

480
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:09,920
This series of lectures with Gu Tangsheng

481
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,680
is really hard to get tickets outside!

482
00:22:12,240 --> 00:22:14,000
Okay, we will go for sure.

483
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:14,560
Good.

484
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,360
Take care sirs.

485
00:22:15,520 --> 00:22:15,920
Goodbye

486
00:22:16,080 --> 00:22:16,960
Take care sirs.

487
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:42,320
Make way!

488
00:22:48,160 --> 00:22:48,880
Everyone go listen!

489
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,160
We know, sir. Okay!

490
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:52,240
Let's go.

491
00:22:54,320 --> 00:22:54,720
Let's go, Old Guo.

492
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:55,440
Keep going, keep going.

493
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,040
Come. Hurry.

494
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,120
Quickly go sit at the front.

495
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,000
Sit at the front.

496
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,360
I'm here. Here, here, here.

497
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:03,040
Come sit here. Sit here.

498
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:13,840
Isn't it?

499
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:16,080
It's hard to get a ticket in the embassy district.

500
00:23:18,080 --> 00:23:19,360
I heard it's like plain boiled water.

501
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,320
Dull.

502
00:23:20,640 --> 00:23:21,280
Go to the front to sit.

503
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:29,600
It's here, it's here.

504
00:24:15,440 --> 00:24:18,640
Students, I know what you all are laughing at.

505
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:21,040
You're laughing at this queue on my head.

506
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:22,560
Everyone look!

507
00:24:45,840 --> 00:24:47,920
What is so laughable about queues?

508
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:50,000
This is our Chinese culture.

509
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,320
A root that cannot be cut off.

510
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,560
All the seated students,

511
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,600
it doesn't matter if you are willing to listen,

512
00:24:57,760 --> 00:25:00,960
as long as you guys recognize you are Chinese,

513
00:25:01,280 --> 00:25:03,680
you will be attached to this queue.

514
00:25:04,804 --> 00:25:06,480
The only difference between us is that

515
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:10,320
my queue is tangible, put on top of my head,

516
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:12,800
your queues are intangible,

517
00:25:13,200 --> 00:25:14,640
concealed in your hearts.

518
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:22,960
Don't at all think that after cutting off hair,

519
00:25:23,600 --> 00:25:25,120
after wearing Western clothes,

520
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,440
have our mouths full of English,

521
00:25:27,920 --> 00:25:30,320
foreigners will think highly of us.

522
00:25:30,560 --> 00:25:31,760
On the contrary.

523
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,280
When a Chinese person

524
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:35,360
westernizes into a foreigner,

525
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:38,800
it will precisely arouse their contempt.

526
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:41,040
Only by letting them see

527
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:42,480
that we Chinese people,

528
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,800
have their own distinctive spirit

529
00:25:45,200 --> 00:25:46,480
and civilization,

530
00:25:47,040 --> 00:25:48,640
only then in their hearts will they have

531
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,800
genuine respect for us.

532
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:56,160
Okay. Next, I will start my lecture.

533
00:26:01,600 --> 00:26:04,960
Students, today the lecture topic

534
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,800
is the Spirit of Chinese People.

535
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:13,360
This topic, I have lectured foreigners many times on.

536
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,280
But the lectures I give them,

537
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:19,120
everyone has to purchase a two silver dollar ticket.

538
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:22,000
Furthermore, I determined not to give them opportunities to interrupt

539
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,680
and raise questions!

540
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,080
Of course, today is different.

541
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,320
I am in Peking University's auditorium,

542
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,800
giving my own students a lecture.

